description: SDK and package management
globs: ["**/*.csproj"]
---

- Target latest LTS SDK (e.g., net9.0).
- Use `PackageReference` for all dependencies.
- Avoid transitive dependencies from legacy packages.
- Lock versions for critical packages (e.g., EF Core, Serilog).
- Use PackageReference format instead of packages.config.
- Specify exact versions for security-critical packages.
- Use Directory.Packages.props for centralized package management.
- Avoid package downgrades unless necessary.
- Use analyzers for code quality and security.
- Keep packages up to date for security patches.